Short:    1.5 PubScreen util, like FrontPS +WB GUI
Uploader: nil (Lee Kindness)
Author:   nil (Lee Kindness)
Type:     util/misc
Requires: WB2+

Lets you set the default pubscreen. Also returns the name of the front screen,
eg `Publican`, Can also write front public screen name to a environment 
variable. Public screen flags can be set, including if screens are to poped 
to the front when a window opens and if windows should open on the default 
public screen.